*12.Ferrobádminton       27  6  3 18  44-78  15  [*]

*[*] Ferrobádminton were not relegated, apparently due to a rule 
*    (the existence of which is unconfirmed) indicating that none of
*    the teams that played in the first championship (1933, which
*    applied to Ferrobádminton as merger of Ferroviarios and Badminton)
*    could be relegated


